NTU LocalProxy:
  NTU (Network Termination Unit) is an idea to forward the connection via TOR.
  NTU can be used for:
  * Hide more the Tor hidden services (forwarding a connection to tor).
  * Connect the applications to Tor network without SOCKS support.
  * Connect yout email client via tor and internet without SOCKS support.
  
  Example of use:
  
  Tor Hidden Service ----> NTU ----> Tor Hidden Service ----> Server.
  Email client ----> NTU ----> Tor ----> Hidden Service.
  
NTU is a part of TorDNSLocalProxy project.

